Lokacin jawabin Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A yau da dare a Wheeling, West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara kamfen dinsa na farko.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau a Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake tabbatar da zaben da za a yi a cikin babban kotu don cike gurbin babban kotun, Trump na neman ya kara goyon baya ga zaben da za a yi a cikin watan Nuwamba, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa ikon su na mulkin majalisa idan aka yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a fara jawabin Trump a West Virginia, kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya Trump zai yi jawabi a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia, a misalin karfe 7 na yammacin Amurka a ranar Asabar 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a bidiyo ta YouTube a kasa.
Trump zai iya yin la'akari da wannan makon na Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke cikin matsala game da tuhumar cin zarafin jima'i, tare da amincewa da Majalisar Dattijai a cikin mako guda a cikin binciken FBI.
Amma ainihin manufar da wadannan jawabai ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican, wanda aka zaunar da su a gaban zaben Nuwamba.
Kamfen din shugaba Trump ya sanar da cewa zai yi jawabai guda biyar a mako mai zuwa da nufin "Taro masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da jam'iyyar Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai".
"Sarrafa majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban har shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama da zai iya, yayin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da tashin hankali", wani jami'in kamfen din Trump ya fadawa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
An shirya taron a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji The West Virginia Metro News.
Asabar ce rana ta biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimaka wa Patrick Morris, dan takarar Sanata daga West Virginia, wanda ke kan gaba a zaɓe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morris cewa shugaban ya zo don gwadawa da kuma ba shi damar yin zabe", in ji Simon Heather, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia.
