Paul Barreiro, farfesa a fannin ilimin kwakwalwa a Harvard Medical School kuma babban daraktan kula da lafiyar jama'a a Harvard, ya ce jami'arsu ta yanke shawarar yin wannan shirin ne bayan sun gano cewa dalibai sukan rasa barci a cikin mako.
