saukar da wani sabon Jamus warship sake jinkirta
Sabon jirgin ruwan na Jamus ya kamata ya shiga cikin 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan Cold War, amma ba za a bayyana ba sai shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ba daidai ba da kuma hauhawar farashi, a cewar kafofin watsa labarai na cikin gida.
An jinkirta saukar da Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgin ruwan sabon nau'in jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, in ji jaridar Die Zeit, tana mai ambaton wani wakilin soja.
An shirya shigar da jirgin cikin 2014, amma matsalolin da suka taso bayan ginin sun hana wannan babban burin.
An yi umarni da jiragen ruwan yaki guda hudu na aji Baden-Wuerttemberg a shekarar 2007 don maye gurbin tsoffin jirgin ruwan Bremen.
Za a yi amfani da makamai masu karfi, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da wasu fasahohin Stealth, kamar rage hangen nesa na radar, infrared, da siginar sauti.
Daga cikin muhimman halaye  mafi tsawo lokaci tsakanin goyon baya  mafi sabon frigates iya kasa shiga tashar jiragen ruwa har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Amma dai, jinkirin da ake samu na nufin jiragen ruwan da za su iya bai wa Jamus damar nuna karfinta a kasashen waje sun tsufa kafin a fara amfani da su, in ji jaridar Die Zeit.
Frigate F125 da aka yi wa rashin farin ciki ya shiga labarai a bara lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus ta yi watsi da karbar jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa ga kamfanin Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan ne karon farko da sojojin ruwa suka dawo da jirgin ruwa bayan da aka kai shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa jirgin ya koma ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun rubuta game da "kuskuren da yawa a cikin software da kayan aiki" wanda ya sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a cikin aikin yaƙi.
The software flaws kasance musamman muhimmanci, kamar yadda Baden-Wuerttemberg aji jirage da kawai 120 sailors  rabin ma'aikatan na haihuwa Bremen aji frigates.
